extends layout

block content
  section.hero
    .hero-text
      h2 Our Story: Saving Good Food, One Deal at a Time
      p Save Before Expiry began with a simple idea—fresh food shouldn’t end up in landfills when it can still feed people and save them money.
      a.btn-primary(href="/dashboard") Explore Nearby Deals
    .hero-image
      img(src="about.jpg", alt="Team working together to reduce food waste")

  section.features
    h2 What We Stand For
    .feature-list
      .feature-box
        h3 Waste Less
        p We rescue quality near-expiry items before they’re tossed.
      .feature-box
        h3 Spend Smart
        p Transparent pricing and countdowns so you know the real value.
      .feature-box
        h3 Trust First
        p Vetted partners, clear freshness info, and honest reviews.
      .feature-box
        h3 Local Impact
        p We help neighborhood stores move inventory responsibly.

  section.reviews
    h2 How We Work
    .review-list
      .review-box
        p "We map surplus inventory to nearby shoppers with timely reminders."
        span - Product & Data
      .review-box
        p "Every partner store is onboarded with quality checks and clear standards."
        span - Partnerships
      .review-box
        p "Designing for clarity keeps shoppers confident about freshness."
        span - Experience

  section.features
    h2 Quick Stats
    .feature-list
      .feature-box
        h3 250k+
        p Items saved from waste.
      .feature-box
        h3 92%
        p Orders rated 4-5 stars for freshness and value.
      .feature-box
        h3 1.2k
        p Local stores and bakeries partnered.
